Document: VirtualJoystick
Path: godot/classes/class_virtualjoystick.rst
Summary: A virtual joystick that can be used for input in games.

Inherits: Control < CanvasItem < Node < Object

A virtual joystick that can be used for input in games. It provides a visual representation of a joystick that the user can interact with by dragging their finger or mouse. The joystick's position and movement are translated into input events that can be used to control game characters or other game elements.
