Summary: Defines the theme properties for the VirtualJoystick, specifying the StyleBoxes for the joystick base and tip in both normal and pressed states.

Theme Property Descriptions
normal_joystick (StyleBox): Base joystick StyleBox.
normal_tip (StyleBox): Tip joystick StyleBox.
pressed_joystick (StyleBox): Base joystick StyleBox when pressed.
pressed_tip (StyleBox): Tip joystick StyleBox when pressed.